ary precautions to guarantee that all personal information is kept safe, including security measures to stop personal information from being inadvertently lost, misused, or accessed without authorization. We restrict access to your personal information to those who actually require it for business purposes. Those handling your information are sworn to secrecy and will only act in ways that have been authorized.</p><p class="fw-light my-3 fs-5">Additionally, we have protocols in place to handle any suspected breach of data security. If We are legally obligated to inform you and any relevant regulator of a suspected data security breach, We shall do so.</p></div><div class="my-5"><h2 class="display-6 fw-normal mb-4">Data Security and Storage</h2><p class="fw-light my-3 fs-5">We take data security seriously and have measures in place to protect your information. Your data is stored within secure systems in compliance with applicable regulations. While we do our best to secure your data, please be aware that internet transmission is not entirely risk-free.</p></div><div class="my-5"><h2 class="display-6 fw-normal mb-4">Your Rights</h2><p class="fw-light my-3 fs-5">Under data protection regulations, you have specific rights related to your personal data. You have the right to access your data, request corrections, and, in some cases, request deletion. You can also object to certain processing activities. If you have any questions or requests related to your data, please contact us at <a href="https://mail.google.com/mail/u/0/?tab=rm&ogbl#inbox?compose=GTvVlcSBmlwGfVkCvjcNcbdTBcCRVjDHlKNHjZBBjWjgVkrDHtjfvmDxCZZVLRjKNGnlRGdRkwvSM" target="_blank">contact@tutorselevenplus.co.uk</a></p></div><div class="my-5"><h2 class="display-6 fw-normal mb-4">Contact Us</h2><p class="fw-light my-3 fs-5">If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding your data or our privacy practises, please don't hesitate to get in touch with us at <a href="https://mail.google.com/mail/u/0/?t